WEBVTT

00:00:28.750 --> 00:00:34.211
TODAY IS JUNE SECOND, NINETEEN NINETY-EIGHT. SURVIVOR: Lube Stal.

00:00:34.555 --> 00:00:37.012
NAME BY BIRTH: Bodgas.

00:00:37.238 --> 00:00:39.479
INTERVIEWER: DAVID Karlin.

00:00:39.479 --> 00:00:42.114
INTERVIEW IS TAKEN IN NEW YORK,

00:00:42.250 --> 00:00:44.052
UNITED STATES OF AMERICA,

00:00:44.052 --> 00:00:45.518
in yidish.

00:00:48.679 --> 00:00:52.166
mir ruft men DAVID Karlin.

00:00:52.577 --> 00:00:53.595
kuf.

00:00:53.595 --> 00:00:55.198
alef. reysh.

00:00:55.198 --> 00:00:56.163
lamed.

00:00:56.163 --> 00:00:57.634
yud. nan, nun.

00:00:57.960 --> 00:00:59.936
haynt, dem tsveytn yun,

00:00:59.936 --> 00:01:01.683
toyznt nayn hundert nayn,

00:01:01.977 --> 00:01:03.844
akht un nayntsikstn,

00:01:04.760 --> 00:01:09.513
ikh nem a intervyu bay froy Lube Stal, geborene Bodgas.

00:01:10.009 --> 00:01:12.061
der intervyu kumt for

00:01:12.135 --> 00:01:13.884
in Nyu-York,

00:01:14.110 --> 00:01:16.165
Fareynikte Shtatn OF Amerike,

00:01:16.165 --> 00:01:17.715
in yidish.

00:01:22.328 --> 00:01:23.925
vi ruft men aykh?

00:01:24.589 --> 00:01:27.654
Libe Shtal Bodgas.

00:01:28.234 --> 00:01:31.552
 kent ir undz zogn in z- oysyes ayer familye,

00:01:31.558 --> 00:01:32.497
yetst?

00:01:33.043 --> 00:01:36.731
mayn, MARRIAGE familye, oder mayn,

00:01:35.659 --> 00:01:37.581
⟨M-⟩ UNK

00:01:36.731 --> 00:01:37.796
mayn meydlshe?

00:01:37.819 --> 00:01:38.910
BY MARRIAGE.

00:01:39.287 --> 00:01:40.395
Shtal.

00:01:40.468 --> 00:01:42.132
in BUKVes, kent ir zogn dos?

00:01:42.510 --> 00:01:43.528
S.

00:01:43.528 --> 00:01:44.338
T.

00:01:44.338 --> 00:01:45.114
A.

00:01:45.114 --> 00:01:46.638
H.L.

00:01:47.691 --> 00:01:49.777
ven zayt ir geborn gevorn?

00:01:50.982 --> 00:01:56.274
FEBRUARY dem fuftsetn, nayntsn tsvey un tsvantsik.

00:01:55.808 --> 00:01:57.824
vi alt zayt ir yetst?

00:01:57.512 --> 00:01:59.818
zeks un zibetsik yor.

00:02:00.364 --> 00:02:02.298
vu zayt ir geborn gevorn?

00:02:02.608 --> 00:02:04.053
in Pruzhene,

00:02:04.228 --> 00:02:05.201
Poyln.

00:02:05.764 --> 00:02:08.799
vos far a groyse shtot iz gevezn nit vayt fun Pruzhene?

00:02:08.294 --> 00:02:13.014
s'hot nisht geven keyn tsu groyse shtot; s'hot geven a bafelkerung arum

00:02:13.223 --> 00:02:14.904
akht toyznt yidn.

00:02:14.674 --> 00:02:17.688
ober vos far a groyse shtot iz gevezn lebn...?

00:02:16.598 --> 00:02:18.718
o, lebn undz?

00:02:18.842 --> 00:02:21.530
 Kobrin iz hot geven a gresere shtot,

00:02:21.530 --> 00:02:24.692
Brisk iz hot geven a gresere shtot.

00:02:25.710 --> 00:02:32.845
un, arum undz iz s-, kh'rekhn az, Baranevitsh hot oykh geven a gresere shtot

00:02:32.845 --> 00:02:34.462
vi Pruzhene hot geven.

00:02:35.700 --> 00:02:40.599
kent ir undz dertseyln vegn ayer lebn, vos ir gedenkt fun ayer kindheyt,

00:02:40.599 --> 00:02:42.546
biz onheyb fun der krig?

00:02:43.125 --> 00:02:44.328
ikh meyn, dos heyst,

00:02:44.328 --> 00:02:46.460
bizn eyn un fertsikstn yor.

00:02:46.669 --> 00:02:49.515
UNK dertseyl⟨n nokh⟩ vegn nayn un draysikstn yor, vi ir zayt...

00:02:49.791 --> 00:02:50.679
bite.

00:02:54.031 --> 00:02:58.897
, di ershte zakh vos ikh gedenk, iz bin ikh geven a yesoyme;

00:02:59.275 --> 00:03:01.243
kh'hob nisht gehat keyn foter.

00:03:01.671 --> 00:03:04.196
mayn tatn hobn polyakn

00:03:05.367 --> 00:03:11.059
derharget. zey hobn im geshosn ven er iz geforn fun eyn shtetl in der tsveyter.

00:03:11.059 --> 00:03:13.075
er hot geven a groyser soykher

00:03:13.075 --> 00:03:15.493
un er hot gehat bay zikh a sakh gelt.

00:03:15.205 --> 00:03:16.498
vi hot er geheysn?

00:03:16.234 --> 00:03:18.118
er hot geheysn Mendl

00:03:18.242 --> 00:03:19.957
Bodgas.

00:03:21.415 --> 00:03:27.562
un, tsu fil gedenk ikh nisht vegn im, vayl ikh bin geven ALMOST fir yor alt,

00:03:28.468 --> 00:03:30.642
ober vos ikh veys,

00:03:30.642 --> 00:03:34.976
altsding vos nokh dem on a tatn hob ikh zikh dervust.

00:03:36.636 --> 00:03:38.621
ven m'hot im geshosn

00:03:38.813 --> 00:03:41.594
iz er geforn mit nokh a por shutfim.

00:03:41.594 --> 00:03:46.231
iz di shutfim hobn im avekgefirt keyn Varshe,

00:03:47.014 --> 00:03:49.542
un in Varshe hot men im operirt;

00:03:49.542 --> 00:03:52.407
m'hot im gedarft araynshteln a nayem gorgl.

00:03:53.443 --> 00:03:56.508
ober oyfn dritn tog iz er geshtorbn,

00:03:57.308 --> 00:04:01.082
un mir hobn absolut gornisht gevust fun dem.

00:04:01.611 --> 00:04:03.118
nor azoy vi

00:04:03.118 --> 00:04:05.084
s'iz geven a kleyne shtetl,

00:04:05.084 --> 00:04:07.480
iz di mame hot aroysgegangen in der fri,

00:04:07.480 --> 00:04:10.484
hot zi gezen, se shteyt gruplekh, azelkhe v-

00:04:10.484 --> 00:04:12.928
kleyne, un me redt, un me veynt.

00:04:13.322 --> 00:04:16.286
un azoy vi zi iz tsugegangen, hot men zikh

00:04:16.495 --> 00:04:18.834
in gantsn tsegangen gegangen,

00:04:18.908 --> 00:04:20.944
bizkl zi hot zikh dervust

00:04:21.507 --> 00:04:24.810
az ir man iz toyt, un,

00:04:26.215 --> 00:04:28.943
un dos hot geven di end fun undzer lebn.

00:04:28.898 --> 00:04:30.630
vi hot geheysn ayer muter?

00:04:29.286 --> 00:04:30.461
s'hot geven...

00:04:30.619 --> 00:04:32.891
mayn mame hot geheysn Sheyndl.

00:04:32.948 --> 00:04:34.632
oyfn meydlshn nomen

00:04:34.632 --> 00:04:36.215
iz zi geven Segel,

00:04:36.829 --> 00:04:39.568
ober oyfn khasene-gehatn nomen

00:04:39.568 --> 00:04:41.655
iz Bodgas.

00:04:43.495 --> 00:04:46.071
zi hot geven eyn-un-eyntsike kind,

00:04:46.836 --> 00:04:49.931
un zi, zi hot undz,

00:04:49.931 --> 00:04:53.275
nisht tsu fil geRAISEt, oder vi zogt in Amerike,

00:04:53.275 --> 00:04:55.521
gehodevet, vi ikh volt zogn oyf yidish.

00:04:55.678 --> 00:04:59.317
ober gehodevet hot undz a bobe, ir mame.

00:05:00.150 --> 00:05:03.485
un zi hot shoyn ongehoybn tsu prubirn

00:05:03.627 --> 00:05:05.657
tsu oyshaltn ire kinder,

00:05:05.657 --> 00:05:08.041
vayle zi hot geblibn mit dray kinder.

00:05:07.828 --> 00:05:09.594
vi hobn zey geheysn, di kinder?

00:05:09.567 --> 00:05:12.683
der ershter iz hot ge⟨hey-⟩ -ven mayn bruder,

00:05:13.110 --> 00:05:14.960
hot er geheysn Mikhl

00:05:15.507 --> 00:05:16.952
Bodgas.

00:05:17.042 --> 00:05:22.436
di tsveyte hot geven a kind vos hot geborn gevorn toyt.

00:05:23.033 --> 00:05:25.170
un nokh dem bin ikh gekumen.

00:05:26.357 --> 00:05:29.675
ikh, kh'hob shoyn gezogt ven ikh bin geborn gevorn.

00:05:29.952 --> 00:05:32.547
un nokh mir iz gekumen mayn shvester.

00:05:32.547 --> 00:05:33.877
ven zi...

00:05:34.423 --> 00:05:40.627
hot geven bloyz dray khadoshim. azoy arum, zi hot in gantsn nisht gekent dem tatn, un nisht gevust.

00:05:40.954 --> 00:05:42.973
vi heyst ayer shvester?

00:05:42.608 --> 00:05:44.779
mayn shvester heyst Golde,

00:05:45.460 --> 00:05:50.499
oyfn meydlshn nomen Bodgas, ober oyfn farheyratn nomen Kenigsberg.

00:05:54.403 --> 00:05:57.451
bar, ikh veys, zeks yor mistame

00:05:57.643 --> 00:06:01.445
hobn mir, hob ikh ongehoybn geyn in shule. mayn bruder hot zikh gelernt

00:06:01.445 --> 00:06:02.666
in a kheyder,

00:06:03.347 --> 00:06:07.394
un nokh dem iz hot er shoyn aroysgegangen helfn der mamen,

00:06:07.394 --> 00:06:10.091
s'zol araynkumen epes parnose.

00:06:10.688 --> 00:06:15.443
ober, i- mir hot men gelernt in a Yavne,

00:06:15.443 --> 00:06:16.824
a Tarbut shul.

00:06:17.083 --> 00:06:19.895
kh'hob geendikt zibn klasn Tarbut shul.

00:06:19.952 --> 00:06:22.511
in velkhe shprakh iz gevezn di Tarbut shul?

00:06:22.348 --> 00:06:23.388
ivrit.

00:06:24.559 --> 00:06:26.166
un m'hot undz gelernt

00:06:26.166 --> 00:06:28.975
eyn sho in tog poylish.

00:06:30.567 --> 00:06:33.396
un az ikh hob geendikt di zibn klasn,

00:06:33.452 --> 00:06:36.500
volt ikh zeyer gevolt zikh lernen vayter,

00:06:36.507 --> 00:06:39.403
ober ikh hob nisht gehat keyn meglekhkeytn.

00:06:39.898 --> 00:06:42.055
bin ikh azoy geblibn in shtub,

00:06:42.055 --> 00:06:43.993
tsugeholfn a bisl

00:06:44.050 --> 00:06:45.208
in der heym,

00:06:46.108 --> 00:06:49.291
un nokh dem iz hob ikh shoyn ongehoybn

00:06:49.500 --> 00:06:51.772
tsu gehern tsu a organizatsye.

00:06:52.352 --> 00:06:55.164
ikh hob gehert tsu Hashomer Hatsair.

00:06:56.115 --> 00:06:59.428
ober s'iz glaykh dokh shoyn geven milkhomes, un

00:06:59.428 --> 00:07:01.863
mayn hofenung iz geven...

00:07:02.224 --> 00:07:04.701
kh'hob nit gevust az s'vet kumen a milkhome...

00:07:04.701 --> 00:07:06.689
az kh'vel forn oyf HAKHSHARA

00:07:06.780 --> 00:07:08.883
un dan, fun dortn vel ikh

00:07:09.042 --> 00:07:10.976
OLE zayn keyn Yisroel.

00:07:10.982 --> 00:07:12.545
ober di ale

00:07:12.585 --> 00:07:16.494
DREAMS, vi zey zogn, khaloymes, iz alts gevorn

00:07:17.361 --> 00:07:18.705
tsu gornisht.

00:07:19.183 --> 00:07:23.480
kent ir undz dertseyln, VOT, ir hot gezogt, ir zayt geven in Shomer Hatsair,

00:07:22.626 --> 00:07:23.497
ye.

00:07:23.689 --> 00:07:26.951
kent ir dertseyln, mit vos hot zikh farnumen di organizatsy⟨e⟩?

00:07:26.951 --> 00:07:28.593
vos flegt ir ton dortn?

00:07:28.852 --> 00:07:32.655
 ikh bin geven a TSEIRA nokh, ikh ken aykh nit dertseyln genoy,

00:07:32.655 --> 00:07:35.563
vayl ikh hob JUST ongehoybn tsu geyn in Hashomer Hatsair.

00:07:35.940 --> 00:07:37.303
di mentshn

00:07:37.303 --> 00:07:40.544
velkhe, di MENAHELIM, di onfirers undzere,

00:07:40.544 --> 00:07:42.366
iz zaynen geven arbetorer.

00:07:42.366 --> 00:07:44.250
eyner hot geven, lomir zogn,

00:07:44.597 --> 00:07:47.426
a TEACHER, a lerer fun ivrit.

00:07:47.533 --> 00:07:50.795
eyner iz hot gearbet bayn tatn, er hot ge-... kh'gedenk

00:07:50.795 --> 00:07:53.040
az ot der tate iz geven a kirzhner,

00:07:53.040 --> 00:07:55.459
hot er tsugenumen dem zun tsu zikh.

00:07:56.241 --> 00:07:58.147
un,

00:07:59.160 --> 00:08:02.102
eyner iz hot, rekhn ikh, Shl⟨e⟩ymovitsh,

00:08:02.102 --> 00:08:05.162
hot geven a lerer in,

00:08:05.505 --> 00:08:08.455
in, nisht in Pruzhene, nor in a ander shtot.

00:08:09.015 --> 00:08:11.705
ot ir flegt zikh trefn, di yugnt?

00:08:10.450 --> 00:08:12.277
mir flegn zikh trefn

00:08:12.277 --> 00:08:13.430
in ovnt

00:08:13.993 --> 00:08:15.340
un,

00:08:15.340 --> 00:08:19.728
mir flegn aroysforn oyf a, ir veyst dokh, oyf a tsuzamentref.

00:08:19.728 --> 00:08:23.016
eyn mol za- bin ikh geven in Kobrin oyf a tsuzamentref,

00:08:23.072 --> 00:08:25.720
un eyn mol bin ikh geven in Pinsk.

00:08:27.966 --> 00:08:32.027
un s'hot, altsding hot geven JUST azoy vi a kholem, vayle

00:08:32.337 --> 00:08:35.993
s'hot dokh glaykh ongehoybn, m'hot geredt az s'vet zayn a milkhome,

00:08:36.352 --> 00:08:39.569
un in nayn un draysikstn yor hot shoyn oysgebrokhn di milkhome.

00:08:39.929 --> 00:08:43.905
az s'hot oysgebrokhn di milkhome, hot men shoyn geblibn in gantsn on gornisht.

00:08:44.402 --> 00:08:45.656
di polyakn

00:08:45.656 --> 00:08:49.341
iz zaynen antlofn gevorn, un s'hot gevorn di shtot

00:08:50.511 --> 00:08:52.088
EMPTY, pust.

00:08:52.148 --> 00:08:55.061
lomir zikh kern a bisl tsurik tsu der tsayt...

00:08:53.920 --> 00:08:54.909
ye.

00:08:55.320 --> 00:09:00.984
 ayere, ayer muter, ayer bobe, ayer mishpokhe iz gevezn a religyeze?

00:08:57.835 --> 00:08:59.014
ye.

00:08:59.367 --> 00:09:00.832
ye, ye.

00:09:00.940 --> 00:09:01.862
ye.

00:09:02.003 --> 00:09:03.836
 kh'hob gehat,

00:09:04.517 --> 00:09:06.485
⟨A⟩CROSS THE STREET fun undz

00:09:06.643 --> 00:09:09.472
iz hot zikh gevoynt mayn tatn's tate,

00:09:09.782 --> 00:09:14.045
un er hot gehat zin. zey zaynen geven farheyrate, mit kinder,

00:09:14.828 --> 00:09:18.764
ober zey hobn zikh nisht gebadert mit undz, absolut nisht.

00:09:19.266 --> 00:09:23.431
 zey zaynen geven, eyner, mayn zeyde hot geven a shuster,

00:09:23.431 --> 00:09:25.802
ober mir hobn gegangen mit tserisene shikh.

00:09:25.802 --> 00:09:29.486
far vos? vayl er hot geBLAMEt mayn mamen,

00:09:29.486 --> 00:09:31.993
far vos zi hot im gelozn forn,

00:09:31.993 --> 00:09:34.093
azoy vi zi volt gevust, oder...

00:09:34.200 --> 00:09:36.506
ober dos iz dos. ir veyst,

00:09:36.850 --> 00:09:40.438
me ken nisht ander- endern di ⟨ni-⟩ mentshlekhe natur.

00:09:41.811 --> 00:09:44.488
ot azoy hobn mir geven

00:09:45.355 --> 00:09:46.651
in gantsn

00:09:46.651 --> 00:09:50.260
on mishpokhe; nor vos mir hobn gehat iz geven di bobe.

00:09:50.181 --> 00:09:51.952
fun vos hot ir gelebt?

00:09:52.206 --> 00:09:54.815
di ershte zakh, hobn mir gehat aleyn a

00:09:55.159 --> 00:09:57.532
k-, beheyme, a ku,

00:09:58.146 --> 00:10:01.802
un mir flegn hobn far zikh milkh, un farkoyfn.

00:10:02.331 --> 00:10:03.827
di tsveyte zakh,

00:10:03.917 --> 00:10:08.804
hobn mir gehat hiner mit katshkes, mit endikes, mit,

00:10:08.912 --> 00:10:14.182
ikh veys,... me flegt dingen bay a goy a shtikl feld,

00:10:14.182 --> 00:10:17.479
un m'hot gezetst a tsibele mit,

00:10:17.479 --> 00:10:20.735
 kroyt, mit, TOMATOES, ⟨m-⟩...

00:10:21.045 --> 00:10:25.882
un THEN flegn mir nokh zeyen un hobn feld kartofl.

00:10:26.580 --> 00:10:29.336
un dos iz hot men gehat, khayune.

00:10:29.336 --> 00:10:31.299
oyser dem iz

00:10:31.710 --> 00:10:34.134
halbe hoyz fun undzer hoyz

00:10:34.140 --> 00:10:35.804
hobn mir gehat far RENT,

00:10:35.804 --> 00:10:38.414
iz hobn mir gehat oyf di shtayern tsu tsoln.

00:10:38.414 --> 00:10:40.954
oyf nokh a por dolar flegt araynfaln

00:10:40.954 --> 00:10:44.141
vos m'hot gekent, lomir zogn, a kind lernen, oder...

00:10:44.147 --> 00:10:46.125
s'hot nisht geven laykht.

00:10:46.425 --> 00:10:48.073
zogt mir,

00:10:48.298 --> 00:10:52.159
di yugnt, VOT, ir hot, UNK Shomer Hatsair, hot ir gezogt.

00:10:51.117 --> 00:10:52.123
ye.

00:10:52.159 --> 00:10:55.852
ir flegt zikh trefn, ir flegt vo- zingen lider, vos flegt ir dortn...?

00:10:56.213 --> 00:10:57.720
 me flegt...

00:10:56.415 --> 00:10:58.788
⟨vi es⟩ flegt zayn bay aykh bay zamlungen azelkhe.

00:10:57.720 --> 00:11:01.016
ye., me flegt zingen...

00:11:01.427 --> 00:11:05.803
v- vayl ikh bin geven dokh nokh zeyer veynik; ikh hob dokh geven a TSEIRA.

00:11:05.803 --> 00:11:08.424
kh'hob JUST arayngetrotn in di organizatsye.

00:11:08.532 --> 00:11:11.414
azoy flegt zayn diskusyes un,

00:11:11.414 --> 00:11:13.582
 me flegt redn un,

00:11:13.582 --> 00:11:15.633
 ⟨f- un⟩ me flegt,

00:11:15.633 --> 00:11:18.889
PLANen ver s'vet avekforn oyf hakhshore,

00:11:18.889 --> 00:11:20.827
zol men aroyshelfn.

00:11:21.019 --> 00:11:24.202
ober ikh hob nokh nisht dergangen azoy vayt.

00:11:24.293 --> 00:11:28.455
un m'iz flegt zingen, me flegt tantsn a hore, a tumba⟨UNK⟩.

00:11:28.647 --> 00:11:30.159
s'iz,

00:11:30.216 --> 00:11:33.529
s'hot geven, a freylekher lebn, un

00:11:33.529 --> 00:11:37.250
s'hot gekost zeyer veynik vos men, mitglids-optsol, efsher

00:11:37.250 --> 00:11:39.308
getsolt fuftsik groshn a monat,

00:11:39.308 --> 00:11:41.786
oder nokh efsher veyniker; kh'gedenk nisht.

00:11:42.822 --> 00:11:43.679
zogt mir,

00:11:43.679 --> 00:11:48.977
 zaynen bay aykh gevezn in Pruzhane, efsher gedenkt ir, zaynen bay aykh gevezn,

00:11:46.770 --> 00:11:47.844
ye.

00:11:48.977 --> 00:11:53.311
nor eyn shul iz bay aykh geven, Tarbut? oder s'iz geven a yidishe shul?

00:11:51.900 --> 00:11:53.475
nor eyne, NO.

00:11:53.475 --> 00:11:56.082
s'iz geven a povshekhne shule.

00:11:55.984 --> 00:11:57.277
in velkhe shprakh?

00:11:56.082 --> 00:11:57.204
dos iz ⟨e-⟩...

00:11:57.204 --> 00:11:58.537
in poylish.

00:11:58.537 --> 00:12:00.629
dortn hot zikh mayn shvester gelernt,

00:12:00.629 --> 00:12:05.191
vayl dos hot geven fun di regirung; dos hot nisht gekost keyn gelt.

00:12:06.143 --> 00:12:09.647
un s'iz geven a folk-shule, a Perets shule,

00:12:10.227 --> 00:12:13.528
a yidishe shul. s'iz geven zeyer a kulturele shtetl.

00:12:13.618 --> 00:12:16.869
in velkhe shprakh hot men dortn gelernt, in Perets shul?

00:12:15.289 --> 00:12:16.852
dortn, yidish.

00:12:18.698 --> 00:12:21.493
 THEN iz geven a hebreishe gimnazye.

00:12:22.309 --> 00:12:24.125
in Pruzhane iz geven?

00:12:22.967 --> 00:12:26.150
ye, ye. s'iz geven a hebreishe gimnazye.

00:12:26.157 --> 00:12:28.395
un fun di arumike shtetlekh,

00:12:28.485 --> 00:12:32.596
vos bay zey in shtetl hobn zey gekent zikh lernen ivrit, ir veyst dokh,

00:12:32.704 --> 00:12:35.510
ober az zey hobn gedarft geyn in gimnazye,

00:12:35.510 --> 00:12:40.143
iz hobn zey shoyn gedarft araynforn in Pruzhene shteyn un zikh dortn lernen.

00:12:40.143 --> 00:12:42.418
un s'iz geven a PAŃSTWOWe gimnazye.

00:12:42.930 --> 00:12:44.966
ir hey- dos heyst a melukhishe?

00:12:43.285 --> 00:12:44.679
oyser dem...

00:12:44.719 --> 00:12:46.282
ye. oyser dem

00:12:46.322 --> 00:12:51.007
iz hobn mir, Pruzhene iz geven zeyer a kulturele; s'hot nit nor geven Hashomer Hatsair.

00:12:51.250 --> 00:12:53.541
s'iz geven a Khalut- Khaluts,

00:12:53.541 --> 00:12:56.545
s'hot geven Algemeyne Tsienistn,

00:12:56.545 --> 00:12:59.144
un Revizyonistn, un

00:12:59.144 --> 00:13:00.694
mikol-haminim.

00:13:02.944 --> 00:13:06.043
ikh ken aykh nit oysrekhenen alts genoy,

00:13:03.552 --> 00:13:04.153
i-...

00:13:06.319 --> 00:13:09.463
ober kh'ken aykh, farshraybn, az ir vet veln,

00:13:09.463 --> 00:13:12.911
vayl mir hobn dos altsding, mir hobn aroysgegebn a pinkes,

00:13:13.086 --> 00:13:15.813
un altsding iz do in dem pinkes.

00:13:16.275 --> 00:13:19.363
zogt mir, ir, ayer m- in ayer mishpokhe,

00:13:18.992 --> 00:13:19.931
yo.

00:13:19.363 --> 00:13:22.749
flegt ir di yidishe yontoyvim opmerkn?

00:13:22.772 --> 00:13:25.314
NO, keyner hot undz nisht ayngeladn,

00:13:25.624 --> 00:13:29.870
un s'hot geven azoy vi mir voltn zikh oysgeR-, -hodevet

00:13:29.944 --> 00:13:31.895
in gantsn oyf hefker.

00:13:32.239 --> 00:13:33.974
absolut nisht!

00:13:33.974 --> 00:13:37.110
ober ven mayn bruder hot shoyn gevorn a bisl elter,

00:13:37.318 --> 00:13:39.365
un er hot zikh dokh gelernt in kheyder,

00:13:39.365 --> 00:13:41.987
⟨iz⟩ flegt er shoyn makhn a seyder,

00:13:42.010 --> 00:13:44.155
oder... ober

00:13:44.389 --> 00:13:46.695
opgehit hobn mir shabes,

00:13:47.663 --> 00:13:52.854
vayle di bobe flegt undz nemen in shul, in besmedresh,

00:13:53.181 --> 00:13:57.056
un, az s'hot geven a yontev, iz hot men opgehit.

00:13:57.450 --> 00:14:02.003
 un s'hot geven a koshere hoyz, s'iz geven milkhiks bazunder

00:14:02.003 --> 00:14:04.329
un fleyshiks bazunder, un...

00:14:05.314 --> 00:14:09.105
ikh veys nit, tsu dos iz azoy interesant,

00:14:09.178 --> 00:14:12.727
ober s'iz geven, vi me zogt in ivrit, KEDIN-UKEDAT.

00:14:12.727 --> 00:14:14.757
altsding hot geven beseyder.

00:14:16.941 --> 00:14:24.953
 ir hot, i- veyst ir nit, in ayer shtot, tsvishn di yidishistn un di vos hobn gelernt in Tarbut,

00:14:23.623 --> 00:14:25.168
o!

00:14:24.953 --> 00:14:27.009
zaynen geven gute batsiungen?

00:14:25.168 --> 00:14:28.426
o, s'hot geve- NO, zeyer shlekhte!

00:14:28.483 --> 00:14:31.454
me flegt zikh arumkrign un arumshlogn.

00:14:31.454 --> 00:14:33.930
NO, s'hot nisht geven keyn gute batsiungen.

00:14:33.930 --> 00:14:37.438
un m'hot dokh geven yunge mentshn; vos hot dos geshpilt a role?

00:14:37.512 --> 00:14:41.584
s'hot nisht gekumen, s'zol kumen politsey, oder zey hobn imetsn

00:14:41.584 --> 00:14:43.980
fararestir⟨n⟩; m'hot zikh arumgerisn,

00:14:43.980 --> 00:14:46.094
yeder eyner hot getsoygn far zikh.

00:14:48.396 --> 00:14:51.832
hot, hot ir bakumen velkhe nit iz dortn tsaytungen,

00:14:51.785 --> 00:14:53.922
SURE. bay undz in sh- in shtot

00:14:52.176 --> 00:14:53.300
zhurnaln?

00:14:53.922 --> 00:14:56.025
iz hot aroysgegangen a tsaytung.

00:14:55.247 --> 00:14:56.878
vi hot zi geheysn?

00:14:56.025 --> 00:14:57.468
"Di Pruzhener Shtime."

00:14:57.964 --> 00:14:59.375
in velkhe shprakh?

00:14:59.319 --> 00:15:00.489
in yidish.

00:15:01.187 --> 00:15:04.336
un in hebreish zaynen gevezn tsaytungen dortn?

00:15:04.832 --> 00:15:06.058
in hebreish?

00:15:04.866 --> 00:15:09.939
NO, az ir hot gevolt, hot ir gedarft ORDERn fun a ander shtot; s'hot nisht geven.

00:15:11.312 --> 00:15:15.761
zogt mir, bikher in yidish zaynen gevezn bay aykh, in ayer hoyz?

00:15:14.147 --> 00:15:15.710
SURE, s'iz geven.

00:15:15.801 --> 00:15:19.440
bay undz in hoyz? zikher hot geven! vos far a hoyz hot ⟨bay⟩...

00:15:19.581 --> 00:15:20.773
 tsu

00:15:20.880 --> 00:15:24.873
di mentshn hobn gekent, tsu zey hobn nit gekent, dos iz hot geven...

00:15:25.504 --> 00:15:30.378
on a, on a, bikhl, on a sider, on a, a tsaytung?

00:15:30.378 --> 00:15:31.691
epes darf men dokh.

00:15:31.917 --> 00:15:33.170
dos iz,

00:15:33.170 --> 00:15:35.347
nishto keyn frage vos s'hot geven.

00:15:35.347 --> 00:15:38.005
MOSTLY, MOSTLY iz hot geven

00:15:38.005 --> 00:15:40.905
ale balebatish, NICE,

00:15:42.058 --> 00:15:43.109
un,

00:15:43.109 --> 00:15:45.106
un s'hot afile geven a yeshive.

00:15:47.340 --> 00:15:49.640
un yeder eyner, vi m'hot nisht gehat,

00:15:49.640 --> 00:15:52.329
flegt men nemen a yeshive-bokher oyf a tog...

00:15:53.230 --> 00:15:55.755
kh'veys nit tsu far aykh iz bakant dos, tsu neyn...

00:15:55.980 --> 00:15:58.491
un der yeshive-bokher hot gekumen esn

00:15:58.491 --> 00:15:59.501
farn tog.

00:15:59.524 --> 00:16:02.980
un, morgn hot er gegangen tsu a ander balebos.

00:16:02.980 --> 00:16:05.267
un dos iz hot geven der lebn azoy.

00:16:05.267 --> 00:16:06.920
ober m'hot dokh nisht nor

00:16:06.920 --> 00:16:08.974
gelebt far zikh; m'hot nokh gedarft

00:16:08.974 --> 00:16:10.489
epes oyfton,

00:16:10.489 --> 00:16:13.338
vi mayn bobe fleg zogn, far oylem-habo.

00:16:15.555 --> 00:16:17.591
s- UNK...

00:16:16.517 --> 00:16:19.531
zaynen geve- vifl, ir gedenkt, vifl zaynen gevezn

00:16:19.656 --> 00:16:24.392
shuln, ikh meyn, ⟨mish-, m- meys-hami-⟩ -midroshim? ye.

00:16:21.900 --> 00:16:23.429
bet-medroshim?

00:16:23.588 --> 00:16:26.400
o, oyf yeder gas iz hot geven tsvey!

00:16:26.895 --> 00:16:29.386
 undzer hoyz iz hot geven,

00:16:29.443 --> 00:16:32.508
 JUST antkegn a besmedresh.

00:16:33.139 --> 00:16:37.177
oyf yedn gas iz hot geven, ober der grester besmedresh hot geven

00:16:37.177 --> 00:16:40.372
Beys Yankev besmedresh. dos hot shoyn geven

00:16:41.037 --> 00:16:43.748
a shenerer, a,

00:16:43.922 --> 00:16:47.673
 dortn fleg kumen a khazn oder...

00:16:47.673 --> 00:16:50.295
iz flegt men geyn hern, di eltere.

00:16:51.364 --> 00:16:54.783
ober ven s'handlt zikh vegn

00:16:54.925 --> 00:17:01.818
kultur, iz Pruzhene, rekhn ikh, geshtanen oyfn hekhstn plats, vi andere gresere shtet.

00:17:01.877 --> 00:17:05.431
zogt mir, tsu aykh flegn kumen artistn, o⟨der⟩ zaynen geven bay aykh...?

00:17:04.577 --> 00:17:08.131
o ye, SURE hot gekumen artistn.

00:17:06.957 --> 00:17:08.149
in yidish?

00:17:09.166 --> 00:17:11.539
MOSTLY iz hot geven yidish.

00:17:11.022 --> 00:17:15.386
ir gedenkt nit, eynike fun zey? neyn? vi me, zey hobn geheysn?

00:17:14.688 --> 00:17:17.454
 ikh veys nit tsu ikh bin afile geven,

00:17:17.454 --> 00:17:19.415
vayle m'hot dokh gedarft batsoln gelt,

00:17:19.415 --> 00:17:20.974
un mir hobn nisht gehat keyn gelt.

00:17:21.267 --> 00:17:24.264
gut vos mir hobn azoy oysgekumen!

00:17:24.574 --> 00:17:26.913
zogt mir, bay aykh zaynen gevezn,

00:17:26.953 --> 00:17:32.887
m-, in di ovntn, ovntn fun di yugnt, vos flegn aleyn shpiln,

00:17:29.923 --> 00:17:30.862
ye?

00:17:33.130 --> 00:17:37.174
vos flegn makhn, dortn zingen lider? a khor iz geven?

00:17:35.914 --> 00:17:38.000
zikher, zikher.

00:17:37.585 --> 00:17:39.773
ir zayt, ir hot zikh oykh farnumen? neyn?

00:17:39.357 --> 00:17:41.350
NO, NO, NO, NO.

00:17:40.302 --> 00:17:41.909
ir hot gezungen?

00:17:41.350 --> 00:17:43.220
NO, kh'hob nisht gezungen, NO.

00:17:41.909 --> 00:17:44.278
ir hot geshribn gedikhtn?

00:17:43.220 --> 00:17:44.196
eyn mol,

00:17:44.196 --> 00:17:46.179
eyn mol bin ikh ye geven,

00:17:46.179 --> 00:17:49.509
vos m'hot, der Kern-KAYEMET hot gemakht a bal,

00:17:50.427 --> 00:17:56.363
a purim bal, iz eyn mol bin ikh geven. far vos? vayle m'hot mir gebetn, zol ikh in a kyosk...

00:17:56.363 --> 00:17:58.250
zey flegn dokh makhn farkoyfn,

00:17:58.257 --> 00:18:01.727
 sode, seltser-vaser, ikh veys,

00:18:01.727 --> 00:18:03.620
oder epes a shtikl CZEKOLADKe,

00:18:03.620 --> 00:18:06.402
zol men makhn a por groshn far di organizatsye.

00:18:06.402 --> 00:18:08.933
dos iz dem eyntsikn mol vos ikh bin geven.

00:18:09.377 --> 00:18:12.167
ober di andere zakhn, kh'hob aykh gezogt, ven,

00:18:12.167 --> 00:18:14.892
az ikh ge- hob nisht tsu fil genosn

00:18:14.892 --> 00:18:16.298
fun mayn yugnt.

00:18:17.740 --> 00:18:22.519
 zogt mir, di batsiungen tsvishn di yidn

00:18:22.519 --> 00:18:25.558
in Pruzhene un di poylishe ⟨OB-⟩

00:18:23.147 --> 00:18:24.204
ye.

00:18:25.558 --> 00:18:28.603
andere nit-yidishe bi- mentshn vos hobn dortn gelebt

00:18:28.603 --> 00:18:30.515
zaynen gevezn gute, vi...?

00:18:29.391 --> 00:18:31.798
NO, nisht tsu gut, NO.

00:18:32.226 --> 00:18:33.615
yeder eyner

00:18:33.615 --> 00:18:37.215
hot, vi me fleg zogn, treyfe blut in zikh,

00:18:37.980 --> 00:18:40.168
un yeder eyner hot,

00:18:40.647 --> 00:18:45.028
az ir hot ge- az m'hot gekent bay aykh epes nemen oder vos, iz

00:18:45.878 --> 00:18:47.407
hot geven OKAY.

00:18:47.548 --> 00:18:51.794
zogt mir, ver zaynen geven ayere fraynd, di fraynd fun ayer bruder?

00:18:52.155 --> 00:18:54.194
di fraynd fun mayn bruder?

00:18:52.155 --> 00:18:55.456
 i- ikh meyn di fraynd, di, di, nu, di khaveyrim.

00:18:54.194 --> 00:18:55.409
ye.

00:18:55.409 --> 00:18:59.298
ye. alts iz hot geven,

00:18:59.298 --> 00:19:02.628
mayn bruder iz hot nisht gehert tsu keyn organizatsye,

00:19:03.343 --> 00:19:05.277
un er hot gehat azoy vi

00:19:06.077 --> 00:19:08.183
di shkheynim,

00:19:08.183 --> 00:19:10.714
iz zey flegn aroysgeyn un...

00:19:10.714 --> 00:19:13.279
ober ikh veys nisht genoy,

00:19:13.279 --> 00:19:14.984
vayle ikh

00:19:14.984 --> 00:19:18.283
fleg nisht geyn tsu fil in ergets,

00:19:18.283 --> 00:19:20.299
BECAUSE vu ir zaynt gegangen,

00:19:20.299 --> 00:19:22.102
hot ir gedarft batsoln,

00:19:22.210 --> 00:19:24.628
un ikh hob layder, layder

00:19:24.628 --> 00:19:25.916
nisht gehat.

00:19:26.310 --> 00:19:28.526
azoy arum az ikh bin geven a bisl

00:19:28.526 --> 00:19:30.236
opgeshtanen fun...

00:19:30.563 --> 00:19:34.168
kh'bin geven yoytse-min-haklal, ikh bin geven a bisl...

00:19:36.402 --> 00:19:37.611
yo?

00:19:36.638 --> 00:19:40.648
zogt mir, zaynen gevezn bay aykh fraynd fun nit-yidn?

00:19:40.840 --> 00:19:42.926
NO! NO.

00:19:43.017 --> 00:19:44.529
NO, mit goyim?

00:19:44.805 --> 00:19:46.428
got in himl!

00:19:46.428 --> 00:19:48.194
s'iz dokh epes,...

00:19:48.096 --> 00:19:50.891
nu, tsum bayshpil, shkheynim gute?

00:19:49.883 --> 00:19:53.558
shkheynim? ye. ober eyn shokhn hot geven a guter,

00:19:53.558 --> 00:19:55.886
un eyn shokhn hot geven zeyer a shlekhter.

00:19:56.348 --> 00:19:59.953
undzer hoyz hot aroysgegangen oyf tsvey gasn:

00:20:00.516 --> 00:20:01.714
der front

00:20:01.714 --> 00:20:04.402
iz hot geven ULICA DĄBROWSKIEGO,

00:20:04.402 --> 00:20:07.069
dos o iz hot geven, un

00:20:07.069 --> 00:20:09.740
di gantse hoyz, azoy vi s'iz geshtanen in der leng,

00:20:09.740 --> 00:20:13.656
hot nokh geven a shtal, vayl mir hobn dokh gehat, kh'hob aykh gezogt, a ku

00:20:14.117 --> 00:20:16.507
un hiner un katshkes un gendz...

00:20:16.682 --> 00:20:19.966
iz aroysgegangen tsu MIESZCZAŃSKe gas,

00:20:20.007 --> 00:20:23.325
un oyf MIESZCZAŃSKe gas hobn zikh gevoynt goyim.

00:20:24.310 --> 00:20:27.797
iz eyner hot a bisl geholfn mayn mamen.

00:20:27.904 --> 00:20:30.311
vos hot er geholfn? mir flegn bay im,

00:20:30.570 --> 00:20:33.854
 dingen a shtikl feld

00:20:33.861 --> 00:20:36.808
un, er flegt undz tseakern un

00:20:37.152 --> 00:20:40.945
me flegt im batsoln, er flegt nemen... kh'veys tsu ikh darf dos dermonen...

00:20:40.945 --> 00:20:46.531
fun shtal aroysCLEANen di ale MANURE, di, er flegt farzeyen far undz.

00:20:46.531 --> 00:20:48.708
nor mir hobn gelebt mit im zeyer gut.

00:20:48.708 --> 00:20:50.088
a fakt iz

00:20:50.128 --> 00:20:51.472
az in geto,

00:20:51.529 --> 00:20:53.295
ven er hot farlozn,

00:20:53.790 --> 00:20:58.610
hot er geveynt, vayl er hot gezogt, mir zaynen tsu gute shkheynim, vos,

00:20:58.785 --> 00:21:01.263
s'iz im a shod, un er hot aleyn nit gevust

00:21:01.263 --> 00:21:02.350
vu er geyt.

00:21:02.350 --> 00:21:04.989
un in geto hot er undz nokh geton a toyve oykh.

00:21:05.417 --> 00:21:07.520
vilt ir, zol ikh dos ⟨aykh⟩ dertseyln?

00:21:06.970 --> 00:21:08.324
shpeter UNK.

00:21:07.560 --> 00:21:08.566
OKAY.

00:21:10.441 --> 00:21:12.971
 in der tsayt,

00:21:13.112 --> 00:21:15.283
UNK beys ir hot gelebt far der krig,

00:21:14.985 --> 00:21:15.907
ye.

00:21:16.032 --> 00:21:19.553
ir hot gelebt in poylishe land, in Poyln ⟨iz⟩ dos gevezn.

00:21:18.765 --> 00:21:19.771
ye.

00:21:19.963 --> 00:21:24.159
vos iz forgekumen in nayn un draysikstn yor, beys s'hot zikh ongehoybn di milkhome?

00:21:24.469 --> 00:21:28.158
in nayn un draysikstn yor, ven s'hot oysgebrokhn di milkhome,

00:21:28.435 --> 00:21:32.783
iz Pruzhene geblibn dray t-... m'hot gevust az s'iz

00:21:32.907 --> 00:21:35.013
shoyn a milkhome oysgebrokhn,

00:21:35.013 --> 00:21:37.575
ober Pruzhene hot geblibn dray teg

00:21:37.935 --> 00:21:39.616
on a regirung,

00:21:41.007 --> 00:21:43.029
un oyfn dritn tog

00:21:43.029 --> 00:21:45.608
iz arayngekumen di rusn.

00:21:45.883 --> 00:21:50.166
un m'hot arumgegangen, di mentshn, aroysgegangen oyfn gas, arayngelofn in shtub;

00:21:50.166 --> 00:21:52.993
m'hot nit gevust vos s'vet zayn, vos se vart oyf undz.

00:21:52.993 --> 00:21:56.002
hobn mir derzen di ershte tankistn,

00:21:56.464 --> 00:21:58.128
zaynen arayngekumen,

00:21:59.333 --> 00:22:03.259
un s'hot altsding tsugegangen zeyer shtil.

00:22:04.159 --> 00:22:07.402
zey hobn nit getshepet keynem, zey hobn gornit gezogt.

00:22:07.402 --> 00:22:10.380
nokh dem hobn zey zikh genumen zikh arumkukn.

00:22:10.555 --> 00:22:12.759
iz undzer hoyz hobn zey tsugenumen.

00:22:12.934 --> 00:22:14.506
far vos hobn zey tsugen-...?

00:22:14.506 --> 00:22:16.204
vayl s'iz geven mer

00:22:16.204 --> 00:22:19.998
vifl di MEASUREMENTs iz,

00:22:21.237 --> 00:22:22.817
hot gedarft zayn.

00:22:23.127 --> 00:22:27.846
hobn zey arayngezetst tankistn; zey hobn aropgebrengt zeyere froyen mit kinder.

00:22:27.852 --> 00:22:30.090
di gantse hoyz hot men bay aykh tsugenumen?

00:22:29.117 --> 00:22:31.738
NO, mir hobn zikh dokh oykh gedarft voynen,

00:22:31.738 --> 00:22:33.785
 undz hot men gegebn di kukhnye

00:22:33.825 --> 00:22:37.416
mit, a tsimer azoy vi a shlof-tsimer. dos iz ales.

00:22:37.416 --> 00:22:39.197
un s'iz geven finef tsimern,

00:22:39.197 --> 00:22:41.534
hot dray familyes nokh zikh gevoynt:

00:22:41.534 --> 00:22:42.701
a LЁTCHIK

00:22:42.701 --> 00:22:43.997
mit zayn froy mit

00:22:43.997 --> 00:22:45.986
di kinder... nu, kh'rekhn

00:22:46.195 --> 00:22:47.843
tsvey kinder hot er gehat...

00:22:47.916 --> 00:22:50.846
un eyn tankist, vos hot geven SINGLE,

00:22:50.953 --> 00:22:56.142
un tsvey, un nokh a tsveyter tankist, hot er gehat a vayb mit a kind.

00:22:56.033 --> 00:23:01.764
zogt mir, vifl zaynen geven in ayer mishpokhe beys m'hot aykh ibergelozn nor eyn kikh un a tsimer?

00:23:01.467 --> 00:23:02.794
vifl hot geven?

00:23:02.496 --> 00:23:03.941
ayer mishpokhe.

00:23:03.188 --> 00:23:03.953
ye.

00:23:03.953 --> 00:23:08.623
 f- bay di rusn? finef mentshn; mayn bobe hot nokh gelebt.

00:23:08.925 --> 00:23:11.214
UNK ⟨gehat⟩ eyn tsimer in gantsn?

00:23:10.613 --> 00:23:14.100
yo. nu, SO WHAT? hot men ge- zikh oysgebet, m'hot aropgenumen

00:23:14.140 --> 00:23:18.083
dem, syenik, un m'hot zikh oysgebet oyf der erd. vos iz?

00:23:18.679 --> 00:23:22.734
iz di mame flegt zogn, "got tsu danken, abi m'hot undz in gantsn nisht aroysgetribn."

00:23:22.734 --> 00:23:24.877
vayl s'iz dokh geven faln vos mentshn,

00:23:24.877 --> 00:23:26.666
zey zaynen geven,

00:23:26.666 --> 00:23:30.688
Bundistn, hot men zey in gantsn bay nakht gekumen un aroysgetribn.

00:23:30.627 --> 00:23:33.623
mir'n zikh kern ⟨tsu- nu⟩, a bi⟨t⟩l tsurik ⟨lomir⟩ zikh kern,

00:23:33.293 --> 00:23:34.114
ye.

00:23:33.623 --> 00:23:36.409
tsu bavayzn vos s'iz forgekumen shpeter.

00:23:36.027 --> 00:23:36.983
ye.

00:23:36.432 --> 00:23:40.415
in der tsayt far dem, farn kumen fun di rusn, far der,

00:23:40.431 --> 00:23:43.749
 f- dem ershtn september fun nayn un draysikstn yor,

00:23:42.760 --> 00:23:43.766
yo.

00:23:43.806 --> 00:23:47.343
zogt mir, in ayer shtot, in Pruzhane,

00:23:45.932 --> 00:23:46.854
yo.

00:23:47.383 --> 00:23:50.409
iz gevezn, hot ir dertseylt, zeyer a sakh,

00:23:50.353 --> 00:23:53.755
organizatsyes mit, ye, yugntlekhe.

00:23:50.409 --> 00:23:52.233
, organizatsyes...

00:23:52.233 --> 00:23:56.636
iz dortn gevezn ⟨a⟩ yidishe KINO, hot ir geku- gezen dortn?

00:23:55.737 --> 00:23:56.961
a vos?

00:23:56.636 --> 00:23:57.502
a KINO?

00:23:57.415 --> 00:24:00.304
a kino? SURE hot geven a kino! vos...?

00:23:59.162 --> 00:24:01.856
ir gedenkt nit vos far a kino iz gevezn?

00:24:01.356 --> 00:24:04.837
yo, ikh bin geven, ober ikh gedenk shoyn nit. SURE,

00:24:04.837 --> 00:24:07.341
in kino bin ikh geven yo a por mol.

00:24:06.958 --> 00:24:08.470
oyf velkhe shprakh?

00:24:09.220 --> 00:24:11.441
oyf, poylish.

00:24:11.194 --> 00:24:13.263
un oyf yidish zaynen gevezn kino?

00:24:13.202 --> 00:24:15.761
NO, oyf yidish bin ikh keyn mol nit geven.

00:24:14.772 --> 00:24:16.338
ir hot nit gehert vegn a-

00:24:16.338 --> 00:24:19.018
-za film vi "A Brivele Der Mamen"?

00:24:18.265 --> 00:24:21.881
o, SURE, far vos hob ikh...? ober kh'hob nit gezen di MOVIE.

00:24:21.881 --> 00:24:22.865
SURE!

00:24:23.293 --> 00:24:25.323
ikh rekhn az,

00:24:24.643 --> 00:24:26.510
ir hot gehert andere...?

00:24:25.323 --> 00:24:27.138
mit Mali Pikon...

00:24:27.138 --> 00:24:28.907
ikh rekhn az mir hobn gehat

00:24:28.947 --> 00:24:30.375
a patefon,

00:24:30.921 --> 00:24:34.324
un mir hobn gehat a plite, un mir flegn koyfn a mol,

00:24:34.566 --> 00:24:37.344
 tsu a geburtstog oder vos, ir veyst,

00:24:37.428 --> 00:24:40.722
a... vi hot dos geheysn? a kastinke, oder...

00:24:40.722 --> 00:24:43.278
kh'hob zikh shoyn fargesn dem nomen vi dos hot geheysn,

00:24:43.278 --> 00:24:45.393
ober kh- SURE hot geven.

00:24:45.923 --> 00:24:48.021
 ikh hob dokh aykh azoy fil mol shoyn bamerkt:

00:24:48.021 --> 00:24:51.013
s'iz geven zeyer a kulturele shtetl.

00:24:51.154 --> 00:24:55.597
s'iz geven fun altsding, nor vos m'hot nit gehat ⟨iz⟩ geven keyn gelt.

00:24:55.761 --> 00:25:00.784
ot lomir zikh kern vider tsurik nokhn dray, n- nayn un draysikstn yor, zaynen gekumen di rusn tsu aykh.

00:24:59.777 --> 00:25:00.766
ye.

00:25:00.958 --> 00:25:05.829
hot zikh in lebn, in kulturishn lebn, bay aykh iz gevezn Hashomer Hatsair...

00:25:04.249 --> 00:25:06.051
hot zikh zeyer geendert.

00:25:05.953 --> 00:25:08.360
vos iz forgekumen mit di vos zaynen gevezn...?

00:25:06.578 --> 00:25:08.259
zeyer geendert.

00:25:08.468 --> 00:25:11.263
di rusn hobn gemakht a

00:25:11.556 --> 00:25:13.755
D.K.A. dos iz, dakht zikh mir, geven

00:25:13.755 --> 00:25:15.766
DOM KRASNOY ARMII.

00:25:16.011 --> 00:25:18.362
iz flegt ir dortn darfn geyn,

00:25:18.362 --> 00:25:21.264
un dortn s'hot geven der yidisher beys-yesoymim,

00:25:21.264 --> 00:25:24.240
un zey hobn aroysgefirt,

00:25:24.533 --> 00:25:28.267
un zey... nisht aroysgefirt, nor zey hobn tsugenumen dem plats.

00:25:28.267 --> 00:25:30.500
un dortn hobn zey gemakht zeyer

00:25:30.878 --> 00:25:32.593
DOM KRASNOY ARMII.

00:25:33.038 --> 00:25:37.504
iz flegt ir dortn darfn geyn. s'iz geven oyf POCZ- oyf POCZTOWA gas.

00:25:37.543 --> 00:25:40.037
ober mir hobn dortn nisht gegangen,

00:25:40.037 --> 00:25:45.539
vayle di mame un di bo-... "mit shkotsim? dortn iz dokh nor goyim!

00:25:45.539 --> 00:25:47.089
vu vestu geyn?"

00:25:47.454 --> 00:25:51.883
UNK iz, hot zikh shoyn a bisl ibergerisn der gantser yugnt,

00:25:51.883 --> 00:25:54.013
nokh oyf erger, nisht ⟨oyf⟩ beser.

00:25:54.317 --> 00:25:56.178
ir hot gezogt az,

00:25:56.178 --> 00:26:00.473
bay aykh zaynen gevezn Bundistn, Tsienistn. vos iz forgekumen mit zey

00:25:57.692 --> 00:25:59.766
RIGHT, ye.

00:26:00.473 --> 00:26:02.124
az di rusn zaynen gekumen?

00:26:01.995 --> 00:26:03.507
Bundistn

00:26:03.615 --> 00:26:07.085
iz, vifl ikh gedenk, hot men zeyer a sakh

00:26:07.227 --> 00:26:10.056
opgemasert un m'hot zey aroysgefirt,

00:26:10.230 --> 00:26:13.076
vayle f- fun vanen veys ikh azoy genoy?

00:26:13.217 --> 00:26:16.535
ikh bin nisht geven azoy arumtsuloyfn un visn,

00:26:16.626 --> 00:26:20.250
nor ven di milkhome hot zikh geendikt, un m'hot gemakht a,

00:26:20.250 --> 00:26:22.593
 Pruzhene⟨m⟩ kolektiv,

00:26:23.190 --> 00:26:26.913
iz zaynen ongekumen zeyer a sakh Pruzhener fun Rusland.

00:26:27.038 --> 00:26:28.250
iz di mener,

00:26:28.250 --> 00:26:30.460
hobn zey nit gevust vu zey zaynen,

00:26:30.460 --> 00:26:32.839
ober andere froyen mit di kinder

00:26:32.839 --> 00:26:34.290
hobn ibergelebt,

00:26:34.290 --> 00:26:36.279
UNK zey hobn gehat, rekhn ikh, oder

00:26:36.370 --> 00:26:41.235
mishpokhe in Amerike oder vos, iz fun di o mentshn hob ikh zikh dervust.

00:26:41.235 --> 00:26:42.945
ober ⟨kh'-,⟩

00:26:44.487 --> 00:26:49.948
ikh veys nisht, ales genoy aykh tsu zogn. kh'hob nisht di minderste anung.

00:26:49.920 --> 00:26:53.052
zogt mir, in Pruzhene far der krig, zaynen gevezn

00:26:53.211 --> 00:26:56.192
sokhrim, raykhe mentshn fun yidn?

00:26:54.662 --> 00:26:58.636
zikher, zikher, s'iz geven raykh, raykhe ⟨m-⟩...

00:26:56.923 --> 00:26:59.887
vos iz forgekumen mit zey az di rusn zaynen gekumen?

00:27:01.682 --> 00:27:02.722
gornisht.

00:27:03.319 --> 00:27:04.556
 farkert:

00:27:04.556 --> 00:27:07.792
az di daytshn zaynen arayn tsu undz

00:27:07.792 --> 00:27:09.455
iz der grester soykher

00:27:09.478 --> 00:27:12.779
iz hot gevorn der eltster fun dem JUDENRAT,

00:27:12.786 --> 00:27:14.180
un er hot geTRYt,

00:27:14.285 --> 00:27:16.537
 oyf vifl er ken,

00:27:16.537 --> 00:27:18.275
tsu oyfhaltn,

00:27:18.275 --> 00:27:20.829
unterkoyfn oder vos ⟨un⟩...

00:27:21.190 --> 00:27:23.988
zeyer balebatishe mentshn. ikh veys nit,

00:27:23.988 --> 00:27:25.841
s'hot geven doktoyrim,

00:27:25.847 --> 00:27:28.476
ober di o, MOSTLY di elite,

00:27:28.476 --> 00:27:30.560
iz ven di daytshn zaynen arayn

00:27:30.560 --> 00:27:32.792
hobn zey zikh genumen zelbstmord.

00:27:33.643 --> 00:27:35.774
zey hobn zikh farmakht in a,

00:27:33.677 --> 00:27:35.156
un beys di rusn...

00:27:35.774 --> 00:27:38.548
 tsimer, bay eynem a dokter,

00:27:38.605 --> 00:27:41.301
un vos zey hobn geton, ober m'hot zey getrofn toyt,

00:27:41.301 --> 00:27:43.605
MOST OF di elite fun Pruzhene:

00:27:43.605 --> 00:27:45.664
doktoyrim, tsvey

00:27:45.664 --> 00:27:48.129
LAWYERS iz geven vos ikh gedenk.

00:27:48.129 --> 00:27:50.107
zey hobn zikh gevoynt bay undz in gas.

00:27:49.793 --> 00:27:51.947
un beys di rusn zaynen gekumen

00:27:52.037 --> 00:27:56.317
hot men nit aroysgeshikt keynem fun di sokhrim, fun di raykhe mentshn?

00:27:55.699 --> 00:27:57.414
NO, NO, NO.

00:27:57.707 --> 00:28:00.958
m'hot aroysgeshikt a por, oyf vifl ikh veys.

00:28:01.217 --> 00:28:05.909
eyner iz hot geven, me, er hot geheysn Yankl der ulaner;

00:28:05.909 --> 00:28:08.264
er hot gedint bay di polyakn a⟨ls⟩,

00:28:08.322 --> 00:28:11.927
in der armey, vos hot geheysn mistame far di ulaner.

00:28:12.372 --> 00:28:14.475
iz im hot men aroysgefirt.

00:28:14.548 --> 00:28:16.854
s'iz geven eyner ⟨Dobus⟩.

00:28:17.417 --> 00:28:20.820
er hot geven zeyer a tayerer yid. er hot geven a sherer,

00:28:20.944 --> 00:28:23.216
un er hot geven azoy vi a feldsher.

00:28:23.290 --> 00:28:27.503
alemen flegt er aroyshelfn, on gelt; er hot nisht gekrign batsolt fun dem.

00:28:27.660 --> 00:28:31.822
der vos hot gehat epes oyfgerisn oyfn fus, oder s'hot vey geton di kop,

00:28:31.913 --> 00:28:33.428
er hot geven der,

00:28:33.428 --> 00:28:35.282
der farzorger fun shtetl.

00:28:35.406 --> 00:28:37.121
im hot men aroysgefirt.

00:28:36.705 --> 00:28:40.103
lomir zikh iberraysn oyf a vayle tsu baytn dem TAPE.

